{
  "stem": "22856.2",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he needed 700 men.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And he was allowed also, to take 300 women.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But if you're asking about that, I have to go a little bit back and say, before we came all into Plaszow area, we used to live in the areas outside Cracow.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "My mother had a small house, 24 kilometers behind Cracow.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And when we were not allowed to live in Cracow, I sent my mother, with my sister and her husband, into this small house 24 kilometers-- Niepolomice was the name of the place.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "A village, I would say.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Later on, when the-- when the German organized transport to that sort of camps, like Treblinka, Belzec, and so on, I brought my mother back to Cracow.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I had the chance to keep her in our non-Jewish place.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But my brothers, who were also with her, unfortunately, they had to go with the transport.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And the transport stopped in the forest for a change of signals.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "They escaped.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "The transport wasn't very much surrounded.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And that was the first thing, what my brothers had done, to ring me back.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "I was working still, in the company.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And they ask what to do.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "So we told them, we know what to do.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Come back to Cracow.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "By that time, Schindler organized a group of 200 young men for work in-- in the-- in [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "That was a place behind the ghetto, but close to ghetto.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "Later on, all these people had a chance to put their families on this so-called Schindler's List.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So my two brothers put on the list myself, my wife, my mother, my sister, and brother-in-law.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So on the 15th of October, as I mentioned, 700 men was put into wagons.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we went to Gross Rosen, or Rosen.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
